snippet.title: Snarf gameplay (PC Game, 1988)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Snarf, Dos PC game produced by Everett Kaser Software in 1988 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/snarf/4316/
Snarf is a fun action game where you try to find your way through a maze without getting overrun. The objective is to finish all levels.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
